Name: SalePrice
Description: the property's sale price in dollars.

Name: MSSubClass

Name: MSZoning
Comments: 分為農業區、商業區、住宅區高密度、住宅區低密度等。

Name: LotFrontage
Description: Linear feet of street connected to property
Comments: 應該是到最近的街的距離

Name: Neighborhood
Description: Physical locations within Ames city limits

Name: Condition1
Description: Proximity to main road or railroad

Name: Condition2
Description: Proximity to main road or railroad (if a second is present)
Comments: 附近的大路(如果鄰近靠近一條以上的大路)

Name: BldgType
Comments: 房內的格局，有可能MSSUbclass部份資訊重疊

Name: HouseStyle
Comments: 房內的格局，比如幾層樓

Name: OverallQual
Comments: 整體建材等品質優劣，Ranking data

Name: MasVnrType
Comments: 砌體貼面種類，石板類型

Name: ExterCond
Description: Present condition of the material on the exterior

Name: BsmtExposure

Name: BsmtFinType2
Description: Quality of second finished area (if present)

Description: Unfinished square feet of basement area

Name: TotalBsmtSF
Description: Total square feet of basement area
Comments: 整個地下室的區域大小

Name: LowQualFinSF
Description: Low quality finished square feet (all floors)
Comments: 整棟樓低品質的部分面積

Name: HalfBath

Name: TotRmsAbvGrd

Name: GarageArea

Name: WoodDeckSF

Name: OpenPorchSF
Description: Open porch area in square feet

Name: EnclosedPorch
Description: Enclosed porch area in square feet

Name: 3SsnPorch

Name: ScreenPorch
Description: Screen porch area in square feet

Comments: 有沒有網球場、電梯等等
